INSERT INTO tb_careerform (id, name, email, mobile, location, years_of_practice, speciality, message, created_at, updated_at, deleted_at) VALUES ('47','Praveen kumar','mmpraveen0802@gmail.com','8248458410','Chennai','1 year','Embryologist','Praveen Kumar.M 
21,Alangatha street Triplicane
Chennai
Mobile No.: 8248458410
e-mail mmpraveen0802@gmail.com

CAREER OBJECTIVE
To improve the success rate of infertile couples.
Streamline current techniques and learn new ART techniques and procedures.
Carry out research on embryo science.
JOB EXPERIENCE
2021-Till date
 Currently working in Komali Fertility Center, Aster Ramesh Hospital as Junior Embryologist.
Assisting senior embryologist in all ART procedures

2020-2021
Worked in Lifecell International as executive in the cryo-preservation department and molecular genetics department.

2018-2019
Production supervisor in Texbiosciences pvt. Limited. Quality checking of raw materials and  finished products of enzymes and animal feeds.
ACADEMIC CREDENTIALS


Course
B.TECH (BIOTECHNOLOGY)
K.S.Rangasamy College of Technology,
Tiruchengode

DAV
Matriculation Higher Secondary School, Choolaimedu

St.John\'s Senior Secondary School & Junior College,
Mandaveli

Central Board of Secondary Education

SKILL ACQUIRED

    ANDROLOGY 
Instructions for semen collection.
Semen Evaluation- Total count, Motility and Morphology
DNA fragmentation assay
Semen preparation for ICSI, IVF and IUI using Swim up Method and Density Gradient method.
         
    EMBRYOLOGY                                                                                 
IVF lab sterile techniques.
Media preparation for IVF & ICSI procedures .
Preparation for Egg collection 
Identification ,grading and denuding of oocyte 
Transfering oocytes in dishes for ICSI procedures 
Fertilization assessment ,scoring and grading and early cleavage check. 
Embryo grading, embryo loading & Embryo transfer

     CRYOPRESERVATION
Freezing and thawing of semen sample.
Profiling of donor semen sample
Freezing and thawing of oocytes and embryos.
Maintaining of cryocan

     MOLECULAR LABORATORY SKILL
Handling and accessioning patient specimens
Preparation of nucleic acids for downstream proces
(DNA/RNA) extractions from biological materials
Processing samples for PCR, qPCR, fragment analysis.

PROJECT

 Study of Effect of Temperature on Sperm DNA Fragmentation
Synthesis of Silver Nanoparticle using marine algae Chlorella choloepium, Scenedesmus ,Anabena.
Study of invitro toxicity for the crude extract of Caesalpania bonduc and Leucus aspera in Humanlymphocytes
CO CURRICULAR ACTIVITIES
Participated in the National Seminar on ‘Biodiversity Conservation:Status, Future and Wayforward’ organized by National Academy of Biological Science(NABS),Chennai on 19th and 20th July 2014 at Department of Biotechnology K.S.Rangasamy college of Technology
Attended ‘IVF Lab Quality Management and Andrology Workshop’ held on 9th November 2014 at Hitech Fertility Service Ltd.,Coimbatore
Undergone training on ‘CytoGenetics’ during January 2015 conducted in Institute of Bio- Medical Research at Chennai.
Attended workshop on ‘Embryology for Beginners’ conducted by Indian Society of Assisted Reproduction(ISAR) on 11th April 2015 at Sri Ramachandra Medical College.
Participated as Delegate in conference 20th National Conference of Indian Society of Assisted Reproduction(ISAR) on 11th and 12th April 2015 at Sri Ramachandra Medical College.
Attended ‘Vitrification Workshop’ for Theoretical and practical Session conducted by Thomas Flarup Sorensen organized by Origio on 20th May 2015 in Chennai.
Participated in National conference on ‘Computational Fluid Dynamics Application in
Biotechnology Processes’ sponsored by DBT, New Delhi and SERB (DST), New Delhi on 18th and 19th August at Department of Biotechnology, K.S.Rangasamy college of Technology,Tiruchengode.
Attended workshop on ‘Sperm Morphology and DNA Fragmentation’ conducted by Daniel R Franken funded by World Health Organisation (WHO) on 22nd August 2015 at Hotel Ramada,Chennai.
Participated as Delegate in conference ‘International Congress of Academy of Clinical Embryologist India’ (ACE) on 18th and 20th September 2015 at Le Meriden Convention Centre, Kochi
Presented a oral presentation on ‘Effect of Temperature on Sperm DNA Fragmentation’ on 18th to 20th September, 2015 at International Congress of Academy of Clinical Embryologists (ACE), at Le Meriden Convention Centre, Kochi
Participated in Project Design Contest of ‘IEEE-Engineering in Medicine and Biological Society (EMBS) Member Meet 2015’ organized by IEEE-EMBS student branch chapter- KSRCT during 21st and 22nd September, 2015 at K.S.Rangasamy college of Technology,Tiruchengode



Participated in Technical Quiz of ‘IEEE-Engineering in Medicine and Biological Society (EMBS) Member Meet 2015’ organized by IEEE-EMBS student branch chapter-KSRCT during 21st and 22nd September, 2015 at K.S.Rangasamy college of Technology,Tiruchengode.
Won First prize in ‘Biolexican Contest’ organized by CARE CLUB at K.S.Rangasamy college of Technology,Tiruchengode.
Attended Entrepreneurship Development Programme at IIT, Madras

ONE CREDIT COURSES COMPLETED

One credit course on ‘Computational Genomics’

Scored 43% in online NPTEL course ‘Biostatistics and Design of Experiments’ during January to March (20 hour Course) conducted by Indian Institute of Technology, Madras.
    TRAININGS AND WORKSHOP

Completed 7 days training in ‘Toxicology of Bioproducts’ from 10th to 16th June 2016 in BioLim Research and Educational Trust at Chennai
Carried out a short term project on ‘Human Karyotype for Diagnosis of Genetic Disorder’ during 14th to 24th June 2016 at Sri Ramchandra University, Chennai.
Completed ‘Short Term Bee Keeping Training’ conducted by State Bee Keeping Extension Centre, Khadi and Village Industries Commission (KVIC), Kuzhiturai during 24th to 28th February 2016 at K.S.Rangasamy college of Technology, Tiruchengode.
Undergone training on ‘Human Sperm DNA Fragmentation’ during 14th to 26th December 2015 conducted in Institute of Bio-Medical Research at Chennai.
Attended workshop on High Security vitrification conducted by Mr.Jean Louis(Irvine Scientific,USA) organized by Cryo-Bio System on 12th June 2014 at Chennai






EXTRACURRICULAR ACTIVITIES

Member of Centre of Academy Research and Employability club (CARE Club)

Editor and webpage designer for Institute of Electrical and Electronics Engineers- Engineering in Medicine and Biology Society (IEEE-EMBS)










